
The usual:

./configure
make && make install

Will install this nugget.  Once installed you need to copy the provided
rzb_yara.conf.sample to rzb_yara.conf.  Additionally you will need to 
provide some more rules for yara.  These should be placed the directory
specified in rzb_yara.conf.  The rules can be placed in subdirs or
linked to if required as ftw is used to walk the rules directory.

